                             Quartier Libian
                    07700 ST MARCEL D'ARDECHE - FRANCE

	Please use only one of these following payment ways :

	- French bank check.

	- Change (French Francs if possible, else equivalent in all
	  CEE change, in US$ or Swiss money; for all three last case,
